order.title: USPA Product 1
order.description: USPA Self Design Men Round Neck Multi-Color T-Shirt. Handcrafted with Cotton. Perfect for Summers. Material Composition Is 93% Cotton, 7% Elastane.
order.content: Designed with overhead movements in mind, this t-shirt offers a full range of motion. It's made of sweat-wicking fabric with a soft, cotton-like feel. Forward-shifted seams reduce chafing in high-sweat areas while a slight droptail hem adds coverage in back.
